rows.label: tlk70000066_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, what kind of treasure d'you think
I should look for next? There are so
many places I want to visit...

rows.label: tlk70000066_04_msg0002
rows.name:
After all, there are countless legends
and folk stories in Alst that have
never been solved!

rows.label: tlk70000066_04_msg0003
rows.name:
I mean, who's to say we couldn't even
make it to Eden if we tried?!

rows.label: tlk70000066_04_msg0004
rows.name:
...OK, maybe that one's not for me.
Climbing isn't really my forte. But as an
adventurer, the idea is kind of tempting!

rows.label: tlk70000066_04_msg0005
rows.name:
I mean, who KNOWS what kind of
treasure could be hidden in a place
like that, right?!
